**Bit** currency China is a fixed-rate exchange where bitcoins can be bought and sold.

The exchange rates are based on the current BTC/USD market rate from [[MtGox]].

The only currency traded for bitcoins by this service is RMB (Chinese Renminbi).

##History

The service was first seen in June, 2011.  The about page shows the exchange as being based on Beijing.  Trades for the exchange are reported on [[Bitcoin_Charts]].

